shorter and more concrete. For example how about discussing a stock or two that
meet your criteria yet would be soundly rejected using traditional metrics, or
vice versa? And cut out all the "I'm not suggesting my ideas are better"
verbiage; if you didn't think your ideas had merit then you wouldn't be here!
